window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>An epic fantasy where King Arthur is a vampire controlled by the curse of Merlin. A journey of love and betrayal, of dark magic, and spicy fun.</p> <p>Camelot was a land of beauty and splendor. A kingdom stable in its rule with its great king and noble knights of the round table.</p> <p>Except for the fact that Arthur and his knights were vampires. When he decided he wouldn't be used as a puppet for the evil Merlin any longer, Arthur set off to break free from his curse and form an army to take down the sorcerer.</p> <p>Along the way, he went up against blood mages, werewolves, and a secret order of dark magic. He formed his coven and rose to a new level of greatness.</p> <p>This is his tale.</p> <p><i>His Dark Knights</i> is the perfect story for fans of the legend of Arthur and such vampire tales as <i>Dracula</i> and <i>Castlevania</i>.</p>"; 
